## 📝 配置示例

### 季节事件配置（season-events.yml）
```yaml
global:
  event-cooldown-seconds: 5
  highest-priority-only: true

spring-events:
  fair-weather-spring:
    type: "FAIR_WEATHER"
    season: "SPRING"
    trigger-temperature: 15.0
    trigger-mode: "above"
    priority: 1
    cooldown-seconds: 30
    effects:
      - "particle:CHERRY_LEAVES"
      - "message:春风拂面，万物复苏"
```

### 节日配置（festivals.yml）
```yaml
festivals:
  spring-festival:
    name: "春节"
    category: "TRADITIONAL"
    date: "01-01"
    enabled: true
    effects:
      - "particle:FIREWORK"
      - "sound:ENTITY_FIREWORK_ROCKET_LAUNCH"
      - "message:恭贺新春！"
```

---

## 🚀 使用指南

### 查看季节事件
```
/seasons event list      # 列出所有事件
/seasons event info      # 显示事件系统信息
```

### 查看节日
```
/seasons festival list   # 列出所有节日
/seasons festival info   # 显示节日系统信息
```

### 使用 PlaceholderAPI 占位符
```
计分板：今日日期: %liseasons_date%
TAB菜单：季节: %liseasons_season% | 温度: %liseasons_temperature%
聊天格式：[%liseasons_term%] 玩家消息
菜单标题：当前节气：%liseasons_term% (%liseasons_date%)
```

